# =============================================================================
# stswasm .gitignore
#
# This repo ships SOURCE ONLY. Game assets, toolchains, and all build outputs
# are excluded. See README.md for how to supply them and regenerate everything.
# =============================================================================

# --- Proprietary game assets (NEVER commit) ----------------------------------
# Slay the Spire is copyrighted by Mega Crit. You must supply your own copy.
desktop-1.0.jar
**/desktop-*.jar
Slay.the.Spire*/
Slay.the.Spire*.zip

# --- External toolchain symlink ----------------------------------------------
# `statics` is a symlink to the sibling ikvmcraft project (dotnet runtime pack,
# emsdk, IKVM image + libs, SDL/mojoAL headers, etc.). See README.md.
/statics

# --- .NET / loader build output ----------------------------------------------
loader/bin/
loader/obj/

# --- Java launcher build output ----------------------------------------------
launcher/out/

# --- Native (Emscripten) build output ----------------------------------------
native/obj/
native/obj-freetype/
native/*.a
native/*.o

# Auto-generated by native/inject_statics.py ("DO NOT EDIT"); regenerate with
# `./build.sh native`.
loader/statics.c

# --- Frontend deploy output (regenerated by `./build.sh deploy` / `sts-jar`) --
frontend/public/_framework/
frontend/public/image/
frontend/public/jars/

# --- Generated launcher jar (produced by `./build.sh launcher`) --------------
jars/stswasm-launcher.jar

# --- Misc build / OS / editor cruft ------------------------------------------
node_modules/
*.log
*.tmp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
